title: Fusion Fantasy: Nine Celestial Maiden Masters From The Get-Go
description: Fusion Fantasy: Nine Celestial Maiden Masters From The Get-Go Ye Xiu awakened the Eyes of the Gods from the start; No matter which superlative technique, it’s at full mastery! “What did you say, it took you tens of thousands of years to cultivate the rank nine immortal swordsmanship? I’m sorry, I just took a look and got full mastery!”. “The flame of the phoenix? The flame of the Vermillion Bird? The soul of the dragon god? Once I look at it, it’s mine!” “What? You say you are the strongest in the universe? I’m sorry, I have nine Celestial Masters for guidance!” In the vast world, who is pretentious enough to be the king? Ye Xiu: “Please call me the pretentious prick king!” 玄幻：开局九个仙女师傅
alternative_titles: 玄幻：开局九个仙女师傅
